OL,6,FHelen Hobbs, who has been managing
OL,7,FCharlcombe Toad Rescue since 2003,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Closing Charlcombe Lane, with
OL,9,Fthe support of the local community,
OL,10,Fhas been a game-changer for our
OL,11,Famphibian population.
OL,13,F"It has meant that toads, frogs and
OL,14,Fnewts have been able to buck national
OL,15,Ftrends and stand a fighting chance of
OL,16,Fflourishing.
OL,18,FShe said: "The biggest challenge this
OL,19,Fyear was that the busiest night of the
OL,20,Fyear was on February 6 ` a week before
OL,21,Fthe road was due to close.
