OL,6,F"In that one night our brilliant
OL,7,Fvolunteers helped 647 amphibians
OL,8,Facross the road but sadly the casualty
OL,9,Frate was much higher than usual
OL,10,Fbecause vehicles could still use the
OL,11,Flane.
OL,13,F"That is why it is so important to
OL,14,Fhave the lane closed for the six
OL,15,Fweeks", she added.
