OL,6,FClimate change is making it more
OL,7,Fdifficult to predict the migration
OL,8,Fseason for toads, frogs and newts,
OL,9,Faccording to conservationists with
OL,10,Fresearch showing that the common toad
OL,11,Fpopulation had declined by 68% in just
OL,12,F30 years.
OL,14,FThis year the peak for amphibian
OL,15,Fmovements was early February but last
OL,16,Fyear it was mid-March.
