OL,6,FThe biggest challenges facing
OL,7,Famphibians today include road traffic,
OL,8,Floss of habitat, such as the
OL,9,Fdisappearance of ponds, and the
OL,10,Ffragmentation of habitats due to the
OL,11,Fintensification of farming and
OL,12,Fdevelopment.
OL,14,FCharlcombe Lane is one of only three
OL,15,Froad closures to help amphibians
OL,16,Facross the UK.
OL,18,FFroglife operations manager Sheila
OL,19,FGundry said: "It's fantastic to see
OL,20,Fthat the numbers of amphibians at
OL,21,FCharlcombe Lane are so good this year.
