OL,6,F"At Charlcombe Lane there is still a
OL,7,Fhealthy population, thanks to the hard
OL,8,Fwork of the toad patrol who rescue
OL,9,Ftoads, frogs and newts even on wet
OL,10,Fwinter evenings.
OL,12,F"The temporary road closure makes a
OL,13,Fbig difference too, as do the
OL,14,Fsurrounding landowners who look after
OL,15,Fthe breeding pond and foraging grounds.
OL,17,F"It is wonderful to have such a good
OL,18,Fnews story of people and wildlife
OL,19,Fworking so well together", she added.
